---
title: "Bézier curve"
date: 2020-10-26
part-of-speech: noun
synonyms: NA
abbreviation: NA
---

Bezier curves are used in computer graphics to draw shapes, for CSS animation and in many other places.

## Example

>He used the Bézier curve to control the direction of the vector's animation.

